<p>As the someone who thought it up, the actual reason was backstory - specifically that the original ancestor of of GRU-P was created as a part of GRU (then, fourth department) because they were investigating the death of Kirov that Stalin suspected Jagoda and his NKVD (which became KGB later) to be involved in. The rest, as they say, is history.</p>
